collectionMetadata.name: Transfer Pricing MAP and APA Cases, Annual
collectionMetadata.description:
Number of transfer pricing Mutual Agreement Procedure (MAP) and Advance Pricing Arrangement (APA) cases and time taken to complete the cases for Financial Year (FY)2013 to FY2022.

* All figures are as at 31 March of each Financial Year.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Transfer Pricing MAP and APA Cases
datasetMetadata.description:
* The balance number of cases for each Financial Year is the sum of Balance brought forward, Received, Completed and Withdrawn / Rejected cases.
* Received refers to cases that have been received and accepted by Singapore.
* Withdrawn / Rejected refers to cases that have either been withdrawn by taxpayers, or rejected by Singapore / treaty partner.
* For MAP cases, the opening balance for FY2022/23 differed from the closing balance for FY2021/22 as there were 3 MAP cases reclassified to treaty MAP cases.

datasetMetadata.name: Time Taken to Complete
datasetMetadata.description: * Figures refers to the time taken to complete the cases with the 'Completed' status in the resource: Number of Transfer Pricing MAP and APA Cases.
